data.description: Ideally located in the stunning Carson Valley, this 20.04 acre property offers a perfect balance of classic Nevada country living and city amenities. The spacious ranch style home offers 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, formal dining, large great room with wet bar and fireplace, a family room with gorgeous high ceilings and another fireplace. New Pergo Outlast+ flooring in the main living areas and new LVP in back bathrooms. Other recent updates/improvements include new patio cover, new sliding door, new well pump (2022), new A/C and furnace (2021) and more. Laundry room equipped for either gas or electric dryer.  Outside you'll find an oversized 3 car garage with additional storage room. There is also a barn/shop with power and new roof (2020).  There is a newly installed grass area with automatic sprinklers. 12.98 AF of underground water rights (abridged to 9.74 since only being used for the drip irrigation. The well has a variable speed agricultural pump with water meter. There is also a livestock watering hole on property. The kitchen sink is equipped with RO system (not for whole house). The large lot offers endless possibilities! All this with fabulous mountain views!
